# Scanner-produced geojson outputs from the admin UI's "Add a collection"
# flow. collections.json is the source of truth; re-running the scanner
# regenerates these files. To intentionally ship a scanned collection in
# the repo, `git add -f mapfiles/<filename>`.
mapfiles/*_footprints_3857.geojson
mapfiles/*_tileindex.geojson

# Bundled sample tile indexes — keep tracked.
!mapfiles/nj_2020_footprints_3857.geojson
!mapfiles/nj_2020_sample_footprints_3857.geojson
!mapfiles/ky_20x20_tileindex.geojson
